---
// src/pages/policies.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Our Policies & Guarantees"
  description="Learn about our commitment to customer satisfaction with our buyback, exchange, return, and free shipping policies."
>
  <section class="container page-section policies-page">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Our Promises to You</h1>
    <p class="text-center large-text">At [Your Diamond Business Name], your confidence and satisfaction are paramount. We stand behind the quality of every diamond and piece of jewelry we offer with robust policies designed for your peace of mind.</p>

    <div class="policy-grid">
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>[Your Buyback Percentage]% Buyback Guarantee</h3>
        <p>We offer a generous [Your Buyback Percentage]% buyback on your diamond jewelry, ensuring your investment retains significant value. Terms and conditions apply; please refer to our full policy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>[Your Exchange Percentage]% Exchange Policy</h3>
        <p>Should your preferences change, we provide a [Your Exchange Percentage]% exchange value on your diamond jewelry. Upgrade to a larger stone or explore a new design effortlessly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>15-Day Hassle-Free Returns</h3>
        <p>Not completely in love? We offer a 15-day return window from the date of delivery. Enjoy a full refund or exchange with no questions asked.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>Free & Insured Shipping</h3>
        <p>Every order includes complimentary, fully insured shipping directly to your doorstep. We ensure your precious purchase arrives safely and securely.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>Certified & Hallmarked Quality</h3>
        <p>All our diamonds are certified by reputable gemological laboratories (e.g., GIA, IGI), and all gold jewelry is hallmarked, guaranteeing authenticity and purity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>Lifetime Warranty & Care</h3>
        <p>Our commitment extends beyond your purchase. We offer a lifetime warranty against manufacturing defects and provide ongoing cleaning and maintenance services for your jewelry.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="section-divider" />

    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Detailed Policies</h2>
    <div class="policy-details">
      <h3>Buyback Policy</h3>
      <p>You can return your diamond jewelry purchased from [Your Diamond Business Name] for a [Your Buyback Percentage]% buyback value at any time. The buyback value is calculated based on the prevailing market price of the diamond and gold at the time of return, less any applicable making charges or taxes. The diamond must be in its original condition, accompanied by its original certification.</p>
      <h3>Exchange Policy</h3>
      <p>We offer a [Your Exchange Percentage]% exchange value for your diamond jewelry. You can exchange your piece for a new one of equal or higher value. The exchange value is determined similarly to the buyback policy. Any difference in value for a higher-priced item will be paid by the customer.</p>
      <h3>Return Policy</h3>
      <p>Our 15-day return policy allows you to return items purchased online within 15 days of delivery for a full refund. Items must be in their original, unworn condition with all original packaging and certification. Refunds will be processed within [Number] business days to the original payment method.</p>
      <h3>Shipping & Delivery</h3>
      <p>Enjoy free and insured shipping on all orders across [Your Delivery Region]. Once your order is dispatched, you will receive a tracking number. We partner with trusted logistics providers to ensure timely and secure delivery.</p>
      <h3>Certification & Hallmarking</h3>
      <p>Each lab-grown diamond is independently certified by leading gemological institutions like GIA or IGI, detailing its 4 Cs. All gold jewelry bears the [Your Hallmarking Standard, e.g., BIS] hallmark, guaranteeing its purity. These certifications are your assurance of quality and authenticity.</p>
      <h3>Warranty & Maintenance</h3>
      <p>All jewelry purchased from us comes with a lifetime manufacturing warranty. We also offer complimentary cleaning and inspection services to keep your jewelry sparkling.</p>
      <!-- Add more detailed policies as needed (e.g., custom order terms, privacy policy link) -->
    </div>
    <p class="text-center mt-4">For any further questions, please <a href="/contact/">contact our customer service team</a>.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Reusing general page-section styles */
  .page-section {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .page-section h1, .page-section h2, .page-section h3 {
    color: #B0A08C;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .page-section p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-divider {
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px dashed #ddd;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  .large-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .policy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .policy-card {
    background-color: #fcf8f3; /* Light gold/cream */
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .policy-card h3 {
    color: #B0A08C;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .policy-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .policy-details {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .policy-details h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #555;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .policy-details p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>